Troubleshooting Common Issues
Issue 1: Service Fails to Start
Symptoms: Service shows "failed" status Solution:

Check service logs: sudo journalctl -u servicename
Verify script permissions: ls -la /path/to/script
Test script manually: sudo /path/to/script
Issue 2: Service Starts but Stops Immediately
Symptoms: Service shows "inactive (dead)" status Solution:

Check if script runs in foreground
Verify Type=simple is appropriate
Add debugging to script
Issue 3: Permission Denied Errors
Symptoms: Permission errors in journal logs Solution:

Check file ownership: ls -la /path/to/files
Verify user exists: id username
Adjust permissions: sudo chown user:group /path/to/files
